Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.01,DogDays-main,sink,0000,0000,0000,,So, next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.55,DogDays-main,gau,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to tune in!
